entries.quest_location_d: 'Ord Mantell has a 26-hour day and 13 satellites surrounding it, along with its twin moons.'
entries.quest_patrol_d: 'The enemy has been vanquished and now I return home, looking forward to a new adventure.'
entries.title: The Return Home
entries.title_d: Return to the Tansarii Point Station and communicate with it to land. You can communicate with the Station by targeting it and typing /comm in spatial chat.
